      "expected_behavior": "Skill executes all 7 phases, identifies 8% deviation in US Equity (overweight), generates 2-3 trades prioritized by tax efficiency, calculates capital gains tax impact, performs cost-benefit analysis, and recommends rebalancing with specific trade list and implementation timeline.",
